View Results Tree - Browser Response Data is not clearing

Once the execution is done, upon clicking on Clear or Clear All, the Response Data is not clearing in the View Results Tree - Browser view. 

Steps to Reproduce.

1. Open any valid test plan and run for one iteration.
2. In View Results Tree, select Browser view.
3. Click on Clear or Clear All.
4. Browser View data is not getting deleted.
